data.description: Check out this Spacious 3-bedroom 2 bath home with a Large Florida Room and an added Bonus Room. This home sits on a large lot in a well-established neighborhood. The kitchen is beautiful with Wood kitchen cabinets and Newer Stainless-Steel Appliances. There is Ceramic tile floor throughout the home which gives it a sleek and modern look. Convenient location and very close to shopping and many local restaurants. look no further and make this home your very own. Roof will be replaced prior to closing with acceptable offer. Home is priced for a quick sale.
